<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.5.8">
<l>kūṭik kūṭiyuṟ ṟārkaḷi runtu</l>
<l rend="indent">kuṟṟam niṟkanaṟ ṟaṅkaḷpa ṟaintu</l>
<l>pāṭip pāṭiyōr pāṭaiyi liṭṭu</l>
<l rend="indent">narip paṭaikkoru pākuṭam pōlē</l>
<l>kōṭi mūṭiye ṭuppataṉ muṉṉam</l>
<l rend="indent">kauttu vamuṭaik kōvinta ṉōṭu</l>
<l>kūṭi yāṭiya vuḷḷatta rāṉāl</l>
<l rend="indent">kuṟip piṭaṅkaṭan tuyyalu māmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before [your] relatives congregate,</l>
<l rend="indent">speaking of [your] virtues and leaving aside [your] faults,</l>
<l>singing as [they] place [you] on a bier,</l>
<l rend="indent">and cover [you] with cloth like a gift for a fox troop –</l>
<l>because the ones with hearts that dance,</l>
<l rend="indent">joining with Govinda who has the Kaustubha jewel,</l>
<l>they will escape, passing over the place [Yama] intended.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
